---
import Icon from './Icon.astro';
---

<section class="box skills">
	<div class="stack gap-2 lg:gap-4">
		<Icon icon="terminal-window" color="var(--accent-regular)" size="2.5rem" gradient />
		<h2>Programmatic</h2>
		<p>Proficient in developing custom, scalable SEO tools and high-performance websites using technologies like Next.js, Node.js, Python, PHP, WordPress, and Shopify. I specialize in building advanced solutions, such as automated keyword analysis tools, enterprise-grade site crawlers, and marketing automation systems that streamline workflows. My expertise combines deep technical SEO knowledge with robust web development, delivering strategies that enhance search visibility, user experience, and business growth.</p>
	</div>
	<div class="stack gap-2 lg:gap-4">
		<Icon icon="trophy" color="var(--accent-regular)" size="2.5rem" gradient />
		<h2>Data-Driven</h2>
		<p>I’m passionate about data-driven SEO and technical optimization. With expertise in custom SEO tools, large-scale site audits, and keyword forecasting, I create strategies that go beyond rankings—they deliver measurable, long-term results. Leveraging tools like Screaming Frog, Google Analytics, and BigQuery, I analyze data, uncover opportunities, and implement advanced solutions to boost visibility and outperform competitors. Let’s harness data, optimize performance, and drive scalable growth together!</p>
	</div>
	<div class="stack gap-2 lg:gap-4">
		<Icon icon="strategy" color="var(--accent-regular)" size="2.5rem" gradient />
		<h2>Strategy-Minded</h2>
		<p>Experienced in crafting comprehensive SEM strategies that integrate Google Ads and SEO. Skilled in user-focused content, site architecture, and meta optimization while building high-quality backlinks and managing outreach campaigns. Using advanced tools, I track performance, increase visibility, and drive conversion-focused growth. Simply put; every strategy is designed to deliver measurable results and client success.</p>
	</div>
</section>

<style>
	.box {
		border: 1px solid var(--gray-800);
		border-radius: 0.75rem;
		padding: 1.5rem;
		background-color: var(--gray-999_40);
		box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);
	}

	.skills {
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		gap: 3rem;
	}

	.skills h2 {
		font-size: var(--text-lg);
	}

	.skills p {
		color: var(--gray-400);
	}

	@media (min-width: 50em) {
		.box {
			border-radius: 1.5rem;
			padding: 2.5rem;
		}

		.skills {
			display: grid;
			grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
			gap: 5rem;
		}

		.skills h2 {
			font-size: var(--text-2xl);
		}
	}
</style>
